review: Though I live in Australia with good dental clinics I still prefer going to Tarnaka Dental Clinic run by Dr. Arjun nd his wife Dr. Prabhuvani. Have been going to this clinic past 32 years when it was run by snr Dr. K U Rao nd now its their kids who run the show. Now its me nd my whole family go there for a very good friendly nd professional dental treatment. Just recently I had 4 periodontal root cleaning and Dr. Arjun nd team did a great job. The pain I had for years has been treated in just a matter of days. I always felt that I was in good hands because he made me feel right at home and as if I was a friend. the support staff here are very gentle and kind to me. They explained very well what was going on. This is a great place to go take care of your teeth. The team was very professional examining and providing with solutions by priority. Tarnaka Dental clinic   is a great place to go take care of your teeth nd cost wise very reasonable nd affordable. Kudos to the team. Would give it a 5* rating...thanks
